node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Lindsay Lohan in Dubai,UAE with @benefitcosmetics, @narsissist, @aveneusa, @proactiv, @arconalosangeles, @isdin, @givenchybeauty, @luciaclinic, and @westmanatelier. May be a closeup of 1 person and long hair.

node.text:
Keeping my skin clean and fresh is so important to me and knowing what suits my skin is fun! 😇 

I love getting cleansing facials at @luciaclinic to keep my skin healthy and glowing 🤍🙂 

On a daily basis, I start my day with moisturizer: @aveneusa and because I have such fair skin I always use spf: @isdin then I conceal with @narsissist and add some @benefitcosmetics color balm for pinkish lips 👄 and @westmanatelier bronze and highlight 🤩 Lastly, I use @givenchybeauty phenomen’eyes mascara and I’m ready for the day 😘 

At the end of the day I cleanse with @proactiv and @arconalosangeles face wipes and apply some @isdin k-ox eye cream and moisturize again 🥰
